
Lembretes SQL, postegreSQL

CREATE DATABASE <db_name>;
DROP TABLE <tb_name>;
psql --help : postegreSQL
\l : List databases 
\d : Describe relations, sequences ... 
\d <name_table> : Describe especific <name_table> table.
CTRL + L : Limpar tela.
\dt : Describe only relations (tables)
\du : List users
\c <db_name> : change database
sudo -u user_name psql db_name : To login without a password, veja [6]
ALTER USER user_name WITH PASSWORD 'new_password'; : To reset the password if you have forgotten, veja [6]





